OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, still wintry on
OL,7,Fhigh ground, then becoming dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells. Winds
OL,9,Feasing and allowing a touch of frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA dry and bright day with some
OL,12,Fhazy sunshine at times, the best in
OL,13,Fthe morning with high cloud thickening
OL,14,Fin the afternoon. Lighter winds, a
OL,15,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
