OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSunny,
OL,6,Fbreezy and warm on Tuesday, though
OL,7,Fcloudier later, some evening rain.
OL,8,FChance of patchy or rain or showers on
OL,9,FWednesday. Sunshine and showers on
OL,10,FThursday.
